  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determinate the utility of staple-line reinforcement on
      lineal gastrointestinal anastomoses.

      Hypothesis: Seamguard device will decrease the incidence of leak and bleeding in digestive
      lineal stapled anastomoses.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
